- @section = "downloads"
- @subsection = "guis"
- @page_title = "Git - GUI Clients"

- content_for :sidebar do
  = render 'shared/book'

%div#main
  %h1 GUI Clients

  %p
    O Git vem com uma ferramenta gráfica com suporte para fazer commits (<a href="/docs/git-gui">git-gui</a>) e para nevegar (<a href="/docs/gitk">gitk</a>), mas existem várias outras ferramentas para usuários buscando uma experiência específica da plataforma.

  %p
    =link_to "Mostrar somente para o meu SO (Linux)", "#", {:class => "subtle-button", :id => "gui-os-filter", 'data-os' => 'linux'}
    %span#os-filter-count
      %strong 0
      %span.os Linux
      GUIs estão destacados abaixo ↓

  %div.two-column
    %div.column-left
      %ul.gui-thumbnails
        %li.mac
          =link_to(image_tag('guis/github-for-mac@2x.png', {:width => '294', :height => '166'}), "http://mac.github.com/")
          %h4= link_to "GitHub for Mac", "http://mac.github.com/"
          %p.description
            <strong>Plataformas:</strong> Mac</br>
            <strong>Preço:</strong> Free
        %li.windows
          =link_to(image_tag('guis/github-for-windows@2x.png', {:width => '294', :height => '166'}), "http://windows.github.com/")
          %h4= link_to "GitHub for Windows", "http://windows.github.com/"
          %p.description
            <strong>Plataformas:</strong> Windows</br>
            <strong>Preço:</strong> Free
        %li.mac
          =link_to(image_tag('guis/gitx@2x.png', {:width => '294', :height => '166'}), "http://gitx.laullon.com/")
          %h4= link_to "GitX (L)", "http://gitx.laullon.com/"
          %p.description
            <strong>Plataformas:</strong> Mac</br>
            <strong>Preço:</strong> Free
        %li.mac
          =link_to(image_tag('guis/sourcetree@2x.png', {:width => '294', :height => '166'}), "http://www.sourcetreeapp.com/")
          %h4= link_to "SourceTree", "http://www.sourcetreeapp.com/"
          %p.description
            <strong>Plataformas:</strong> Mac</br>
            <strong>Preço:</strong> Free
        %li.mac.windows.linux
          =link_to(image_tag('guis/smartgit@2x.png', {:width => '294', :height => '166'}), "http://www.syntevo.com/smartgit/index.html")
          %h4= link_to "SmartGit", "http://www.syntevo.com/smartgit/index.html"
          %p.description
            <strong>Plataformas:</strong> Windows, Mac, Linux</br>
            <strong>Preço:</strong> $79/user / Free for non-commercial use
    %div.column-right
      %ul.gui-thumbnails
        %li.mac
          =link_to(image_tag('guis/tower@2x.png', {:width => '294', :height => '166'}), "http://git-tower.com/")
          %h4= link_to "Tower", "http://www.git-tower.com/"
          %p.description
            <strong>Plataformas:</strong> Mac</br>
            <strong>Preço:</strong> $59/user (Free 30 day trial)
        %li.mac
          =link_to(image_tag('guis/gitbox@2x.png', {:width => '294', :height => '166'}), "http://gitboxapp.com/")
          %h4= link_to "Gitbox", "http://www.gitboxapp.com/"
          %p.description
            <strong>Plataformas:</strong> Mac</br>
            <strong>Preço:</strong> $19.99 / Free for personal use
        %li.windows
          =link_to(image_tag('guis/git-extensions@2x.png', {:width => '294', :height => '166'}), "http://code.google.com/p/gitextensions/")
          %h4= link_to "Git Extensions", "http://code.google.com/p/gitextensions/"
          %p.description
            <strong>Plataformas:</strong> Windows</br>
            <strong>Preço:</strong> Free
        %li.mac.windows.linux
          =link_to(image_tag('guis/git-cola@2x.png', {:width => '294', :height => '166'}), "http://git-cola.github.com/")
          %h4= link_to "git-cola", "http://git-cola.github.com/"
          %p.description
            <strong>Plataformas:</strong> Windows, Mac, Linux</br>
            <strong>Preço:</strong> Free

  %div.callout
    %p
      Existem outras ótimas ferramentas GUI disponíveis. Matthew McCullough mantém uma excelente lista de <a href="http://delicious.com/matthew.mccullough/git+gui">Git GUIs</a> organizada por sistema operacional (<a href="http://delicious.com/matthew.mccullough/git+gui+windows">Windows</a>, <a href="http://delicious.com/matthew.mccullough/git+gui+macosx">Mac</a>, e <a href="http://delicious.com/matthew.mccullough/git+gui+linux">Linux</a>).

